=https%3A%2F%2Fhosted.weblate.org%2Faccounts%2Fprofile%2F%23auth%253E\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://hosted.weblate.org/accounts/profile/#auth%3E\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e disconnect\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe session remains active on the device in step 2. So I continue with a valid session from credentials not linked to any account at \u003ca title=\"https://hosted.weblate.org\" href=\"/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhosted.weblate.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://hosted.weblate.org\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003ePlease check it.\u003c/p\u003e\n","weakness":{"id":27,"name":"Improper Authentication - Generic"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[],"allow_singular_disclosure_at":"2017-06-16T14:16:24.639Z","allow_singular_disclosure_after":-111595523.57967617,"singular_disclosure_allowed":true,"vote_count":3,"voters":["eveeez","brdoors2","spetr0x"],"severity":{"rating":"low","author_type":"Team"},"structured_scope":null,"abilities":{"assignable_team_members":[],"assignable_team_member_groups":[]},"can_edit_custom_fields_attributes":false,"activities":[{"id":1631804,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::BugTriaged","message":"Is seems that session cycling which happens on password change is not applied when removing third party authentications and it's causing this.","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003eIs seems that session cycling which happens on password change is not applied when removing third party authentications and it\u0026#39;s causing this.\u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-04-24T19:10:28.475Z","updated_at":"2017-04-24T19:10:28.475Z","actor":{"username":"nijel","cleared":false,"url":"/nijel","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":